## Technology Stack

- **Frontend**: Angular 18.x, TypeScript 5.5.4, RxJS 7.8.1, @bmc-ux/adapt-angular 18.24.0
- **Backend**: Java 17 (OpenJDK), OSGi, JAX-RS, Spring 5.3.42, Jackson
- **Platform**: BMC Helix Innovation Studio 25.4.00+

## AI Agent Workflow

1. Read [Getting Started](../../cookbook/01-getting-started.md) to understand project structure
2. Assess the requirement — use [Requirement Gathering](../../cookbook/13-requirement-gathering.md) if scope is unclear
3. Check [Best Practices](../../cookbook/09-best-practices.md) before writing code
4. Read the specific cookbook section for the artifact type
5. If the cookbook section lacks detail, read the linked detailed reference
6. After implementation, run through [Checklists](../../cookbook/10-checklists.md)
7. Build and deploy using [Build & Deploy](../../cookbook/08-build-deploy.md)
8. If issues arise, consult [Troubleshooting](../../cookbook/11-troubleshooting.md)
